<SPAN class=headtext>Dear CES Exhibitors and PR Agencies,</SPAN>
<P>The warm weather has kicked into high gear, and we hope you are staying cool! With the start of the summer, it's time to start planning for the 2008 International CES. This year's show will run January 7-10, 2008, and there's already plenty of preparation to be done to ensure a successful International CES experience.</P>
<P>The Exhibitor PR newsletter&nbsp;is distributed monthly to keep you up-to-date on the latest 2008 International CES PR opportunities.</P>
